These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
Beverage: juice, tea
Color: azure, green
1. Beverage:tea is on the left or right of Beverage:juice##3
2. Color:green is on the right of Beverage:tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice |
| Color       | azure | green |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
House: craftsman, colonial
Sport: golf, surfing
1. Sport:surfing is on the left or right of House:colonial##3
2. House:colonial is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| House   | craftsman | colonial |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################
 
